  "text": [
    "Don\u2019t get me wrong: I know",
    "that knowledge is power,",
    "that mystery\u2019s water,",
    "that hunger makes",
    "a gargantuan",
    "lover,",
    "and yes, I\u2019ve drunk",
    "of the river Lethe,",
    "from the breath of the Celts,",
    "from the echo of",
    "the bugling elk,",
    "and yet,",
    "alas,",
    "here I be,",
    "small and twee,",
    "all liquored up",
    "on song and love,",
    "hard as rails",
    "and light as air,",
    "expecting the heavens",
    "to throw down a flare,",
    "to send in the clowns,",
    "to burn a bush,",
    "strike up the sea,",
    "anything",
    "that might mean",
    "those cloudy bastards",
    "have noticed me."
  ],
  "title": "Vanity Flare",
  "year": ""
